<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB01452</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT ESTABLISHING THE MAGNA CARTA FOR BARANGAYS, PROVIDING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to propose the following:
1. Barangay officials including barangay tanods be considered as regular government employees with fixed salaries, allowances and other fringe benefits, including retirement benefits, and membership to Pag-ibig, PhilHealth and GSIS that regular government employees are entitled to; and
2. Every barangay be provided with basic priorities such as regular supply of clean and potable water, transport services, schools, health centers and barangay hall.
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BAGATSING, CRISTAL L.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-04</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Lazatin (000 2019-09-09)</td><td>2. Savellano (000 2019-11-12)</td><tr><td>3. Dalipe (000 2019-12-16)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2019-07-24</td></tr></table>